description:
This hymn karaoke is perfect for lowkey girls who want to sing their hearts out to the amazing He hideth my soul!
Whether you're a Leia fan or not, this song is sure to bring happiness and joy to your heart. Sing along with us in this low key karaoke session, and feel the amazing power of the Force!

Author : Fanny Crosby (1890)
Music performed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube channel.
